Package com.example.sprite.Models

Class Entrant

java.lang.Object
com.example.sprite.Models.User
com.example.sprite.Models.Entrant
public class Entrant extends User
Represents an entrant user who can register for events and receive notifications when selected from waiting lists.

Entrants have the ability to:

  • Register for events and join waiting lists
  • Receive notifications when selected from waitlists
  • Accept or decline invitations to events
  • View their event history

This class extends User and maintains lists of registered events and notifications specific to the entrant.
